data.description: Well cared for ranch style home placed on a quiet street just a couple blocks away from Moville's golf course. The lot is almost half an acre, and there is a storage shed in the backyard. There is also a good sized porch and patio in the front of the house that is perfect for relaxing and has access to the garage through a side door. The deck in the backyard is accommodating and has tree cover that provides great peace and privacy. When you enter the house through the front door you will encounter a sizable foyer/office/bonus living room that has an extra storage closet and a view of the front yard. You will then see the eat-in kitchen that is wide open to the dining/living room. The kitchen features SS appliances, multiple pantry doors, and a tiled backsplash. The dining room and majority of the main floor has new paint, trim, LVP flooring, and new life time warranty windows have recently been installed. The living room comes with an electric fireplace, and there's a door between the living and dining room that will lead you to the back deck. There are two bedrooms and two bathrooms on the main floor. The impressive master bedroom boasts a 6x8 WIC and a 5x15 master bathroom. The master bathroom has a double granite vanity with a stone backsplash. The basement has massive spaces and a wet bar that would be ideal for entertaining. There is another bedroom in the basement with a double closet. The laundry room is also located in the basement and has entrances to the utility room and basement bathroom. This house has a lot to like!
